<paragraph id="8BF936B40D41FFF871CDBC8EFEC87485" blockId="2.[151,1437,152,990]" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis id="B932EAA60D41FFF871CDBC8EFDEE75AE" bold="true" box="[198,549,731,757]" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">Ecology and distribution:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C464D370D41FFF8732EBC89FCEB75AE" authorityName="Schafer-Verwimp. A. Plant" authorityYear="2012" box="[549,800,732,757]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lejeuneaceae" genus="Cololejeunea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Porellales" pageId="2" pageNumber="11" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="tamasii">
<emphasis id="B932EAA60D41FFF8732EBC89FCEB75AE" box="[549,800,732,757]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">Cololejeunea tamasii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from the 
<typeStatus id="54FD88160D41FFF8754CBC89FBB275AD" box="[1095,1145,732,758]" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
collection, at a roadside within a protected area of lower montane rain forest where secondary woody vegetation was dominant. The plants were growing epiphyllous on leaves of shrubs in a humid environment, half exposed to sunlight and therefore drying up periodically. The 
<typeStatus id="54FD88160D41FFF8737BBD05FD6E7431" box="[624,677,848,874]" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
locality itself may be destroyed in the near future as woody vegetation along the road is cleared periodically. However, as a pioneer species 
<taxonomicName id="4C464D370D41FFF87560BD22FB2374CB" authorityName="Schafer-Verwimp. A. Plant" authorityYear="2012" box="[1131,1256,887,912]" class="Jungermanniopsida" family="Lejeuneaceae" genus="Cololejeunea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Porellales" pageId="2" pageNumber="11" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="tamasii">
<emphasis id="B932EAA60D41FFF87560BD22FB2374CB" box="[1131,1256,887,912]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">C. tamasii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, though easily overlooked due to its small size, may possibly be found at similar sites elsewhere in 
<collectingCountry id="F35176240D41FFF875BDBDC8FADD74EC" box="[1206,1302,925,951]" name="Panama" pageId="2" pageNumber="11">Panama</collectingCountry>
or Central America.
</paragraph>
